{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "bc684ecc-44e2-4f4f-a268-cb0af13c70f4",
    "name": "Science1-10-Big Boom",
    "sceneId": "4c80661d-0537-46d4-b6d6-422313186fac",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "a60a2f83-323e-4691-b331-f2c12bb33d9a",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "82792747-d752-4b45-bed4-a01bdaa66d14",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "0178e212-f65a-4fb7-804b-41d374525e04",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Today, we're really going to have a blast!",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "8331f191-8079-4df2-ae31-a1a635821788",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "We shall put your knowledge of Chemistry and Physics together today to create a Big Boom. ",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "8798c046-d3d6-4995-90d7-06ab6161a478",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "text": "This proximity bomb packs more than three times the explosive power of a standard Boom. (Of course, it takes three times as much raw material as a standard Boom, too.)",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "c8491285-8251-4669-ac98-9fe2b75e7353",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "The Big Boom takes three doses of Sulphur, Phosphorus, and Charcoal combined with a little naphtha. This is a highly volatile mixture and should only be combined under rigorous laboratory safety measures.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "8b10ea3f-bbfc-456f-93cb-95e197ceff95",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Kids, don't try this at home.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "170c53ea-1adf-47d6-bd05-89359b6c3102",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "The mixture is then contained in these specially created ceramic containers that allow the Big Boom to be set to explode upon contact. ",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "33bc4094-f3ac-4d54-ba73-53f4b14b3499",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "The Big Boom can be disarmed once it has been set, but be very careful. The slightest mistake and you might find <i>yourself</i> disarmed - literally speaking.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "27cd8967-f6b5-40a0-a0e6-048f97632512",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Are there any questions before we get started?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "e689cab1-9c15-42b7-b54c-f9326823f53e",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "bf0ff65c-e8c0-4e94-910f-836cecf45cf0",
                            "text": "Ask About Chemistry and Physics",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "1d04d7bc-014c-4ef0-b0df-db36f3d2bc9b",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "35",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "7e1d5561-7924-48fa-9260-b2859ba047d8",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "3828eda8-c355-45c5-8bed-81f4cb698ab3",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "How does this combine Chemistry and Physics? Isn't the explosion primarily a chemical reaction?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d8056286-e9ca-459e-8b44-8c3e8496ee58",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Chemistry creates and explains the explosion. Physics describes and determines the results of the explosion. Using the principles of Physics, we can predict the resulting force of the explosion so that we don't inadvertently blow ourselves up.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "f710917d-1e12-4646-bdbd-89f823fe23db",
                            "text": "Ask About the Big Boom",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "bc25f6b5-8d54-4287-91d9-650a8af07f5e",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "35",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "a3200650-8c9a-47f2-9f45-d7abe9c07a75",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "2bca4126-af42-4f18-950c-3d6214a96b0a",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "Just how explosive is a Big Boom? Will we be blowing holes in the castle walls with it?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "fa939d9f-01cf-4d1e-b64e-03afacf1af3c",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "By Archimedes! A Big Boom with the power to blast walls would be far too volatile and dangerous to carry around with you. You might wind up in Timbuktu (parts of you, anyway).",
                                    "emotion": "4",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "04d141ba-655a-4999-82a1-327975edf2b3",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Now, if there were an obvious flaw to the structure of the castle wall, in theory several Big Booms set off at the same time could collapse the wall. However, inside the castle is probably not the best location in which to test out the theory.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "4ec641ba-a22f-4ef4-b818-169eaf4ca0e7",
                            "text": "Say Something Humorous About Science Class",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "43bafadc-5c30-4f94-b9c8-86b783ab431f",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "35",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "a7765225-fe51-4204-9f88-68bffd77112b",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "08fc1993-ff6c-4030-99c7-812f8e58c9da",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "So, if the Big Boom goes up with a bang and a cloud of smoke, would you say this class was all about 'Boom and Plume?'",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "4801ca88-f63e-4ca1-b550-57dfa2c2893c",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I'd probably warn you all to be very careful in class today because oxidants happen.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "3",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "916ac065-3c3a-4e8f-978c-84255c763903",
                            "text": "Say Nothing",
                            "nodes": [],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
